data.text:
1987-1989

Comedy

Watchlist

The caped cartoon crimefighter---a kind of Superman with a tail---won the hearts of millions with the cry, 'Here I come to save the day,' later immortalized by Andy Kaufman on 'Saturday Night Live.' The mouse was featured in an Oscar-nominated cartoon and the series 'The New Adventures of Mighty Mouse and Heckle and Jeckle' and 'Mighty Mouse: The New Adventures,' from 'Fritz the Cat' director Ralph Bakshi.
